title: The Illegitimate Who Devours Weapons
summary: The Illegitimate Who Devours Weapons Manhwa 무기 먹는 서자님 Using his “ability to absorb the memories of a weapon” as a foundation, Lee Cheol would train and go down a path of struggle. His growth would bring about these things, bringing hardship upon Lee Cheol. Life itself would be a struggle for Lee Cheol, and this is his destiny. But in order to protect himself and his surroundings—in order to protect everything—as the fight continues, he’ll unravel secrets from his past life, one by one…!
